The character that was once an oddball with a heart is now more of a grinch version of Alan that he uses to project and solve within himself.  I feel like in the pursuit of answering the questions that bothered him he lost what made the show fun and special. I'm not saying I want a sugar happy clean version of captain d. I understand, requests can get to you, online discourse can be annoying, but if you change your art to tell them off who really won in the end? I don't see the captain disillusion of today telling me to love with my heart and use my head for everything else.
